freeware and shareware products
-------------------------------

  permission is granted to include the following files to the
  distribution of your freeware and shareware products:

  mysticview.library        - 68020/68030, without FPU
  mysticview.library_FPU    - 68030/68040, with FPU
  mysticview.library_68060  - 68060

  your installation script has to install the appropriate version
  automatically, and it must not overwrite newer versions unless the
  user decides to do so.

  since render.library and guigfx.library are required for
  mysticview.library to work, you may also include these libraries
  to your installation. refer to the legal informations provided
  with the respective distributions.
  
  you must refer to mysticview.library in your documentation or
  during installation, or within the executable part of your
  product.
  
  this licence is always implicit and automatically granted for
  freeware and shareware products, as long as you follow the
  restrictions stated above. this licence is not transferable to
  commercial products. if the legal status of your product changes,
  you have to renew your licence.


